%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant O as Omnibox
    participant SE as Site search registry
    participant T as Template engine
    participant Net as Browser nav

    U->>O: Type "j 123" + space
    O->>SE: Lookup "j" prefix
    SE-->>O: Match → Jira template
    O->>O: Enter search mode
    U->>O: Press Enter
    O->>T: Substitute %s with "123"
    T-->>O: Resolved URL
    O->>Net: Navigate
    Net-->>U: Jira ticket page
